<Link id="l01954" /><CodeLine lineNumber="1954"><span class="doxyHighlightComment">  /// Generate unpacklo/unpackhi shuffle mask.</span></CodeLine>
<Link id="l01955" /><CodeLine lineNumber="1955"><span class="doxyHighlight">  </span><span class="doxyHighlightKeywordType">void</span><span class="doxyHighlight"> <a href="/docs/api/namespaces/llvm/#a79354a2324d1cc1c1fd42e5d8a771479">createUnpackShuffleMask</a>(EVT VT, SmallVectorImpl&lt;int&gt; &amp;Mask, </span><span class="doxyHighlightKeywordType">bool</span><span class="doxyHighlight"> <a href="/docs/api/namespaces/llvm/#a9ac8e4e13ad96a39c3f8db9ed633ad2baff50b4aa1c9cc2197ef898436641c911">Lo</a>,</span></CodeLine>

<Link id="l01957" /><CodeLine lineNumber="1957"></CodeLine>
<Link id="l01958" /><CodeLine lineNumber="1958"><span class="doxyHighlightComment">  /// Similar to unpacklo/unpackhi, but without the 128-bit lane limitation</span></CodeLine>
<Link id="l01959" /><CodeLine lineNumber="1959"><span class="doxyHighlightComment">  /// imposed by AVX and specific to the unary pattern. Example:</span></CodeLine>
